.SH "NAME"
git-instaweb \- Instantly browse yo' hustlin repository up in gitweb
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
.nf
\fIgit instaweb\fR [\-\-local] [\-\-httpd=<httpd>] [\-\-port=<port>]
               [\-\-browser=<browser>]
\fIgit instaweb\fR [\-\-start] [\-\-stop] [\-\-restart]
.fi
.sp
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
A simple script ta set up gitweb n' a wizzy server fo' browsin tha local repository\&.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.PP
\-l, \-\-local
.RS 4
Only bind tha wizzy server ta tha local IP (127\&.0\&.0\&.1)\&.
.RE
.PP
\-d, \-\-httpd
.RS 4
Da HTTP daemon command\-line dat is ghon be executed\&. Command\-line options may be specified here, n' tha configuration file is ghon be added all up in tha end of tha command\-line\&. Currently apache2, lighttpd, mongoose, plackup n' webrick is supported\&. (Default: lighttpd)
.RE
.PP
\-m, \-\-module\-path
.RS 4
Da module path (only needed if httpd is Apache)\&. (Default: /usr/lib/apache2/modules)
.RE
.PP
\-p, \-\-port
.RS 4
Da port number ta bind tha httpd to\&. (Default: 1234)
.RE
.PP
\-b, \-\-browser
.RS 4
Da wizzy browser dat should be used ta view tha gitweb page\&. This is ghon be passed ta the
\fIgit web\-\-browse\fR
helper script along wit tha URL of tha gitweb instance\&. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. See
\fBgit-web--browse\fR(1)
for mo' shiznit bout this\&. If tha script fails, tha URL is ghon be printed ta stdout\&.
.RE
.PP
start, \-\-start
.RS 4
Start tha httpd instizzle n' exit\&. Regenerate configuration filez as necessary fo' spawnin a freshly smoked up instance\&.
.RE
.PP
stop, \-\-stop
.RS 4
Quit tha httpd instizzle n' exit\&. This do not generate any of tha configuration filez fo' spawnin a freshly smoked up instance, nor do it close tha browser\&.
.RE
.PP
restart, \-\-restart
.RS 4
Restart tha httpd instizzle n' exit\&. Regenerate configuration filez as necessary fo' spawnin a freshly smoked up instance\&.
.RE
.SH "CONFIGURATION"
.sp
Yo ass may specify configuration up in yo' \&.git/config
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
[instaweb]
        local = true
        httpd = apache2 \-f
        port = 4321
        browser = konqueror
        modulepath = /usr/lib/apache2/modules
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp
.sp
If tha configuration variable \fIinstaweb\&.browser\fR aint set, \fIweb\&.browser\fR is ghon be used instead if it is defined\&. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. See \fBgit-web--browse\fR(1) fo' mo' shiznit bout this\&.
